  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This adversarial package contains an orphan Claim node (W-EP-01): the Claim is richly described and referenced via bindsClaim but carries no prov:wasDerivedFrom link to any Evidence node. ValidationResults carry full provenance chains; the Claim itself does not.",
